{"tid":732853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貿易戰，美國到底要錢定要命？","createTime":"2018-07-07T09:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T13:30:51.000Z","uid":109462,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3ee5984ddd9cb814ad60102a8c67ff54986673d7","tid":732853,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:14:26.000Z","msg":"由中共對媒體嘅指示去睇，已經可以窺探出中共已經預備好要「在維持政府威信嘅情況下體面地對美妥協」，貿易戰基本上係輸硬，但問題係侵侵到底要錢定要命？如果只係要錢、要產業回流，咁經濟雖然崩潰，但江山仲係中共嘅；但如果侵侵當咗自己係列根嚟攞中共條命，咁就大鑊了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>【官媒批評有文章挑動極端情緒】<br />\n【製造中國是「天下第一」的錯覺】<br />\n<br />\n過去大半年，內地傳媒經常出現一類型的標題：「美國害怕了」、「日本嚇傻了」、「歐洲後悔了」......<br />\n<br />\n還有「中國放的這句狠話，美國再聽不懂就要出大事了」、「中國創下多個世界第一.....」、「中國科技實力超越美國，居世界第一.....」等等。<br />\n<br />\n在貿易戰前夕，官媒《人民網》連發三篇文章，指過去這些報道是「浮誇自大文風」，形容「跪求體」、「哭暈體」、「嚇尿體」的文風污染輿論生態，扭曲國民心態。文章指，中國取得了舉世矚目的發展成就，但並非甚麼都能用來自誇，片面地出現「天下第一」的錯覺。<br />\n<br />\n文章又指國家不會因為自大而變強，挑動極端情緒、肆意傳播偏見，容易令公眾走進夜郎自大，自吹自擂的狂妄誤區。以逞口舌之快的形式謀求「精神勝利」，只會混淆是非黑白、顛覆公眾認知。<br />\n<br />\n曾經在官媒任職記者的鄧聿文認為，《人民網》的文章顯示體制內部分人開始發現，以強硬文宣應對貿易戰會被看成是「笑話」，中國政府會被視為「外強中乾，只敢說狠話，不敢應對」。<br />\n<br />\n但鄧聿文認為，這些「浮誇文風」，其實都是跟從官方口徑，「比如外交部、商務部在前期在應對美國貿易摩擦的時候，說的狠話也不少，像甚麼『奉陪到底』」，所以他認為，這不是媒體自身的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1777220885755723/?hc_ref=ARQBg4sr9Dwq5DPXc3_e60drJ9NJRB1MBnY9nuDakZK6ru6dYoaHdDtNQN2KXILUcIg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1777220885755723%2F%3Fhc_ref%3DARQBg4sr9Dwq5DPXc3_e60drJ9NJRB1MBnY9nuDakZK6ru6dYoaHdDtNQN2KXILUcIg&d=hJQBhlW6AHDNPwc9SijFlSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=162d042b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1777220885755723/?hc_ref=ARQBg4sr9Dwq5DPXc3_e60drJ9NJRB1MBnY9nuDakZK6ru6dYoaHdDtNQN2KXILUcIg</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"105a7137760183654a92207b3bfc96bbcea4546d","tid":732853,"uid":85659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留名睇廿年後 美國佬將黑人總統入冊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4009f8962cf22af078ec1d0af61d42e57f82b70","tid":732853,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"105a7137760183654a92207b3bfc96bbcea4546d","tid":732853,"uid":85659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留名睇廿年後 美國佬將黑人總統入冊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T10:23:40.000Z","msg":"入冊不至於，但一定變過街老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a45ec0cbf4995940c134f5e88527a367250505","tid":732853,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T10:30:26.000Z","msg":"why not both?"},{"pid":"62fb5a665ac518b3dc45461420b443c8c7e9e478","tid":732853,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T10:40:16.000Z","msg":"要你支那守返入世規矩都攞你命啦<br />\n根本唔洗講錢<br />\n等同叫個罪犯自首"},{"pid":"8d22968b961d64b8d97c3101210c0a5712d228b7","tid":732853,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T11:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/07/190600_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F07%2F190600_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=8f347e71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3f53b902e4ab2c96093b4003e385604433f810e","tid":732853,"uid":92194,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T11:07:54.000Z","msg":"支那玩串咗個party<br />\n本來安守本份改善經濟民生自己國內點玩都冇人想理<br />\n依家有人透過滲透其他國家政經層面去輸出意識形態<br />\n而且影響力越來越大"},{"pid":"ae35b5dca8fb5a3dda80c190cc24b8f74ab8ba76","tid":732853,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T11:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca1b8ff7c3c3818228f96e8c36bf131a7b872ce","tid":732853,"uid":41545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T13:29:10.000Z","msg":"侵侵今次擺明想攞你命啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢十幾年玩到咁串咀<br />\n唔直接收你皮同放虎歸山有乜即分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf9019087c41c50a5888ae67773e5561358b534","tid":732853,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T13:30:51.000Z","msg":"錢要命都要<br />\n最好剷除支那共産黨"}]}